{"title":"Moto defy Mac 上无法连接 adb 问题","date":"2013-02-10T16:00:00.000Z","link":"Moto-defy-Mac-上无法连接-adb-问题","comments":true,"tags":["android"],"categories":["代码"],"updated":"2020-04-15T21:36:20.851Z","content":"<p>还在用一代神机 defy，虽然已经老的不行，价格从入手时的 2k 掉到现在 150软妹币，用来调试程序还是可以的。<br>速度至少比模拟器快不少吧。另外就是老态龙钟的 defy 还有幸刷上了第三方提供的 android 4.4 rom。</p>\n<p>defy 通过 usb 插上电脑后，在终端中输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">adb devices</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>发现社设备列表没有出现defy。<br>查了下问题，找到了解决方法。<br>在终端中输入</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">system_profiler</span> SPUSBDataType</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>查看系统所有 usb 设备信息。<br>找到手机的Vender ID，记录下来。<br>打开用户目录下的.android/adb_usb.ini文件，把上面的 Vender ID 输进去，保存之。<br>重启下 adb 服务，重新插拔下 usb。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">adb <span class=\"keyword\">kill</span>-<span class=\"keyword\">server</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">adb <span class=\"keyword\">start</span>-<span class=\"keyword\">server</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>再执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attribute\">adb devices</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>时就可以看到设备了。</p>\n<p>reference:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://blog.csdn.net/duanyipeng/article/details/8836040\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://blog.csdn.net/duanyipeng/article/details/8836040</a></p>\n<p>Brought to you by PressCoders.com!</p>\n","prev":{"title":"常用框架集合","link":"常用框架集合"},"next":{"title":"为 VPS 添加 ssh 公钥","link":"github-请求超过限制"},"plink":"https://wuwb.github.io/Moto-defy-Mac-上无法连接-adb-问题/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"吴文斌","link":"<a href=\"https://wuwb.github.io/Moto-defy-Mac-上无法连接-adb-问题/\" title=\"Moto defy Mac 上无法连接 adb 问题\">https://wuwb.github.io/Moto-defy-Mac-上无法连接-adb-问题/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}